{"type": "article", "id": 25705, "title": "玻璃油灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-20T07:00:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607111420q0NlUrfahWLnX6jB.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这盏灯是传统油灯的升级，灯的中心用铝罐装有生物酒精作为燃料，陶瓷纤维做灯芯，通过外火点燃。灯光反射在椭圆形的玻璃灯罩上，像一个小的灯笼，可以手提着走过。发出的热量可以转换成电量储藏在电池中，通过 USB 接口帮助手机充电。设计师 Francisco Gomez Paz 是在意大利工作的阿根廷人，为丹麦品牌 Astep 而设计。产品刚刚在米兰设计周上展出。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111418pLXTADda3muito9S.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111418KWYZgyiFS8t0LdQp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111419qWntDA2Y1Ma5ZeSx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.05448718\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111419N4Geh7Ht2nYXbRDj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.16880342\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}